  "body": "If we want to guard ourselves from these two scenarios:\r\n1) Client has connected, but then got into a deadlock or something, and stopped sending anything to the server\r\n2) Firewall silently dropped connection between client and server, and server waits for commands that will never come\r\n\r\nWe can have ping/pong going regularly from server to the client to detect such situations and terminate hanging connections\r\n",
